	[autofit, sfnt] Fix for `make multi'.

	* src/autofit/afshaper.c: Include FT_ADVANCE_H, to use
	FT_Get_Advance() in it.
	* src/sfnt/ttcmap.c: Include FT_SERVICE_POSTSCRIPT_CMAPS_H
